description.narrative: The Green Tanning Initiative (GTI) in Ethiopia intends to encourage tanneries to move from conventional methods towards chrome-free leather processing and improved working conditions. The 2021 national election and Covid-19 restrictions have hindered the implementation of some activities, nevertheless the project mitigated this by conducting activities virtually and supporting Covid-19 prevention and containment measures.
